description: Politicians in Prague vote to rename a square by the Russian Embassy to honour a slain Putin critic.
title: Nemtsov: Prague denies renaming square to troll Moscow
title_page: Nemtsov: Prague denies renaming square to troll Moscow - BBC News
maintext: "It's very, very important to keep the name in the public domain, for the next political leadership of Russia to have the responsibility to investigate this murder, to have it on the agenda," CNN quoted her as saying.
